Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:05.68,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mini战国basara2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:10.79,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉！！月夜的片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.09,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美的星空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.37,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:36.21,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比传闻中的还要厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.25,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿甲斐之虎的谋略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:43.92,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反施于武田军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.67,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:50.70,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以统帅为打倒织田而组织起来的东国大军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.54,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在这片田里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.26,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我击飞到了遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.67,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你严重地推迟了丰臣军一统日本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.90,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并进军世界的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:31.12,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这责任可是非同小可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.82,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:40.90,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是出类拔萃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.75,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我片仓小十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:50.38,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今生还没见到过你这么大的茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:51.61,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.72,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.96,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也错得太离谱了 片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:15.95,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:20.45,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟看到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.15,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹中半兵卫？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:24.88,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这厮什么时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.23,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是不爱听人说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.30,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许进我家田！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.51,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不要惹我哦
